data.subject: ComfyUI
data.question: What is the function of the Make Square Node custom node?
data.answer: It pads an image to make it square with a chosen filling strategy.

data.subject: ComfyUI.TextEncodeAIO
data.question: How does the TextEncodeAIO node differ from the A1111 extension?
data.answer: The text encoding behavior of the TextEncodeAIO node is inspired by the A1111 extension.

data.subject: ComfyUI.Installation
data.question: How do I install the comfy-pants custom nodes?
data.answer: Clone the repo to the `custom_nodes` folder and install the dependencies using pip.
